      "content": "everything just feels so empty lately. like, i look at everything—the stars, the people, even my own life—and there’s just nothing there. no meaning, no point, no cosmic plan. it’s just this massive, cold, indifferent void that doesn't care if i exist or not. it's hard to even bother waking up when there's literally nothing waiting on the other side of the day.",
